== [[noun]] ==
# a group of two or more words which include its own [[subject]] and [[predicate]] within the expression but as a whole form only a part of a complete sentence. (e.g. ''When it got dark, they went back into the house'', "When it got dark" is the clause within the complete sentence). 
# a separate part of a contract, a will or another legal document.

